=*Shortlisting follow-up email suppressed (reply detected).*

*Subject:* {{$json.prep.subject}}
*Thread ID:* {{$json.prep.threadId}}
*External replied?* {{$json.prep.anyExternalReply ? 'yes' : 'no'}}
*Internal replied?* {{$json.prep.anyInternalReply ? 'yes' : 'no'}}
*Last message from:* {{$json.prep.llmSeed.latestFrom.name || $json.prep.llmSeed.latestFrom.email || 'unknown'}}
*Non-repliers remaining:* {{($json.prep.nonRepliers || []).map(r => r.email).join(', ') || 'none'}}
